metadata.title: Alaska Science Center Publications Database

creators.name: U.S. Geological Survey (USGS), Biological Resources Division, Alaska Science Center (ASC)

metadata.description: This database contains citations and abstracts but does not include the full article text.  The citations provided should be used to locate the full content of a particular publication.  This database cannot be considered exhaustive, especially for publications early in the Center's history.
